PCI: controller: dwc: Do not let PCIE_DW_PLAT_HOST default to yes

PCIE_DW_PLAT_HOST does not have any platform dependency, so it should
not default to yes.

Fixes: 1d906b22076e12cf ("PCI: dwc: Add support for EP mode")
